[D] Lead Times:  Uniform(3–14) days, seeded=42 (reproducible)
[E] Promotions:  Flagged when price < 85% of 30-day rolling avg
[F] EOQ:         sqrt(2 × D × S / H); ordering cost=£50, H=20% of price
